data.description: MULTIPLE OFFERS RECEIVED - Call to Offers by Thursday 12/14/23 at 12pm.    Nestled within the sought-after Sorento community, this 4-bed, 3-bath DR Horton home, built-in 2018, embodies comfort and convenience. Welcoming you inside is a versatile front bedroom and full bath.    Experience a seamless flow throughout the home, featuring a spacious kitchen overlooking the living areas, perfect for gatherings. Additional bedrooms and baths offer flexibility, while the tucked-away master suite ensures peaceful retreat, complete with a substantial walk-in closet.    Step outside to a generous backyard, offering ample space for your personal touch. Embrace the Sorento lifestyle - a coveted location across from scenic Lake Pflugerville, offering trails and outdoor enjoyment.    Conveniently positioned in Pflugerville, this residence invites you to embrace community living and create lasting memories. Don't miss the chance to make this yours!    Note: this property features an ASSUMABLE VA loan at a 2.75% RATE that can be combined with a loan or the remainder. This offers a qualifying buyer better buying power and keeps your monthly payment low (per lender, the buyer does not need to be a veteran to assume the loan).
